Class FixBarcodeAbstractArgumentCollection

  • java.lang.Object

    public abstract class FixBarcodeAbstractArgumentCollection
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Abstract argument collection for fixing barcodes that are encoded in different places than the RTReadUtils.RAW_BARCODE_TAG tag.
